title: Content-field & governance introspection (GH-241/242/236)
description: "Combine GH-241 (pm-7snq stats field-utilization), GH-242 (pm-hntj field-existence filters), GH-236 (pm-mfl1 governance missing-field filters). Shared primitive in core/governance. Philosophy: project management = context management — make under-contextualized items queryable."
